{"title":"歌唱鸠山红专大学","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱鸠山红专大学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动考试"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间工地是战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决心意志是力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起锨镢当武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大战苦干比钢强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地翻了二尺深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五亩地全翻完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种上棉花争丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百斤皮棉定丰产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生“三不靠”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半工半读办法好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建窑来把石灰烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗衣、育苗、打小工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自给自足找门道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"副业收入二千三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办学读书“三不靠”。（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）“三不靠”即不靠国家、不靠农业社、不靠家庭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤俭办学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天王山，红专校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活全凭自己搞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高坡陡羊肠道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃水也得下山挑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑水吃，不辞劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人一天二十挑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖野菜，副食找，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节约粮食吃得饱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做个有志气的青年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有志青年比决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设祖国献青春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立下大志要锻炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力争红透又专深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦学苦练头悬梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设山区扎富根。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}